<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Let=E2=80=99s do=C2=A0an FTX lightning round:<=
/p>
<ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;"=
>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Due to=C2=A0some combination of the s=
peed of its collapse and the casualness of its accounting and governance, <=
