uct a rough =E2=80=9Cbefore last week=E2=80=9D balance sheet that is like $=
14 billion of customer liabilities, $6 billion of liquid assets, $4 billion=
 of illiquid assets, and $14 billion of FTX-associated tokens, for a total =
of $24 billion of assets and $10 billion of net equity. (Then you subtract =
